{"expireTime":9007200917365139000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-a5ff4c1cab526e335d4156f911b11732-gatsby-remark-responsive-iframegatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-external-linksgatsby-remark-header-custom-idsgatsby-remark-code-replsgatsby-remark-embed-snippetgatsby-remark-use-jsxgatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-smartypants-","val":"<h3 id=\"how-do-i-add-css-classes-to-components\"><a href=\"#how-do-i-add-css-classes-to-components\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>איך אני מוסיף CSS classes לקומפוננטה שלי? </h3>\n<p>העבר מחרוזת ל-prop <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">className</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-jsx\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-jsx\"><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu navigation-menu<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">תפריט</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>זה נפוץ ש-CSS classes תלויים ב-props או state של הקומפוננטה:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-jsx\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-jsx\"><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> className <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'menu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isActive<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    className <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">' menu-active'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>className<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">תפריט</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>טיפ</p>\n<p>אם לעיתים קרובות אתה מוצא את עצמך כותב קוד כזה, ספריית <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/classnames#usage-with-reactjs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">classnames</a> יכולה לפשט זאת.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"can-i-use-inline-styles\"><a href=\"#can-i-use-inline-styles\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>האם אני יכול לכתוב inline עיצוב? </h3>\n<p>כן, ראה את התיעוד על עיצוב <a href=\"/docs/dom-elements.html#style\">כאן</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"are-inline-styles-bad\"><a href=\"#are-inline-styles-bad\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>inline עיצוב הוא רע? </h3>\n<p>CSS classes בדרך כלל טובים יותר לביצועים מאשר inline עיצוב.</p>\n<h3 id=\"what-is-css-in-js\"><a href=\"#what-is-css-in-js\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>מה זה CSS ב-JS? </h3>\n<p>“CSS ב-JS” מתייחס לתבנית שבה CSS מורכב בעזרת JavaScript במקום להיות מוגדר בקובץ חיצוני.</p>\n<p><em>שים לב שהפונקציונאליות הזאת היא לא חלק מ-React, אך מסופקת מספריות צד שלישי.</em> ל-React אין דיעה על איך עיצוב מוגדר; אם יש ספק, נקודת התחלה טובה היא להגדיר את העיצוב שלך קובץ <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">*.css</code> חיצוני כרגיל לפנות אלייהם באמצעות <a href=\"/docs/dom-elements.html#classname\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">className</code></a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"can-i-do-animations-in-react\"><a href=\"#can-i-do-animations-in-react\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>האם אני יכול לעשות אנימציות ב-React? </h3>\n<p>ניתן להשתמש ב-React להנפשת אנימציות. ראה <a href=\"https://reactcommunity.org/react-transition-group/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">React Transition Group</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/chenglou/react-motion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">React Motion</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/react-spring/react-spring\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">React Spring</a>, או <a href=\"https://framer.com/motion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Framer Motion</a> לדוגמא.</p>"}